 move 25px\"&gt; foo &lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nThe full description of the syntax is available on the project documentation page\r\n\r\nMore details you can find in our article about this library','Frontpage Animations','','inherit','open','open','','1805-revision-v1','','','2014-05-14 13:01:24','2014-05-14 13:01:24','',1805,'{$page_url}/?p=1809',0,'revision','',0),(1928,1,'2014-05-19 13:45:33','2014-05-19 13:45:33','To achieve the parallax background with overlaid text or other content; start by creating another subpage to your frontpage template. This subpage should be on its own; it should not have any further subpages. Then, add a featured image, and add text to the WYSIWYG editor. The featured image will be used to create the parallax background, and the text in the editor will be added as an overlay to the image, as in the example below:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/parallax_screen-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1900\" src=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/parallax_screen-2.png\" alt=\"parallax_screen 2\" width=\"1343\" height=\"560\" /></a>','Parallax background element','','inherit','open','open','','1927-revision-v1','','','2014-05-19 13:45:33','2014-05-19 13:45:33','',1927,'{$page_url}/?p=1928',0,'revision','',0),(2243,1,'2014-06-22 11:20:11','2014-06-22 11:20:11','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur nibh lacus, lacinia a odio vitae, elementum ultricies lacus. Vestibulum fermentum lorem nec sollicitudin aliquet. Nam eu rhoncus urna. Etiam felis ipsum, luctus et eros sed, bibendum gravida tellus. Mauris tincidunt quis elit ac consequat. Fusce ut elit feugiat, congue nisl at, cursus odio. Morbi pharetra sem ut turpis pellentesque pretium. Aenean nec magna neque. Nulla rutrum porttitor elit, at blandit risus consectetur sed. Donec eu faucibus tellus. Cras varius nunc massa, a eleifend eros feugiat a.\n<h4\">Mission &amp; Purpose</h4>\n<p style=\"color: #666666;\">Inte