/06/gk_image_show_conf.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2296\" src=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/gk_image_show_conf.png\" alt=\"gk_image_show_conf\" width=\"436\" height=\"644\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\"></p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\">The widget configuration is very easy.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\">First of all, you have to specify slides used– you have to put media titles separated with a comma – as you can see we have named our slides as “slide_1″,“slide_2″.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\">Next options are connected with slider width and height on desktop, tablets and mobile devices.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\">The “Pagination” option enables the pagination on the bottom of the slider.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #555555;\">Next three options are strictly connected with the animation speed (speed of the slides transition), interval (time between two slides) and autoanimation (if you need to autoanimate your slides).</p>','GK ImageShow','','inherit','open','open','','2231-autosave-v1','','','2014-06-22 21:08:18','2014-06-22 21:08:18','',2231,'{$page_url}/2231-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(2296,1,'2014-06-22 21:07:32','2014-06-22 21:07:32','','gk_image_show_conf','','inherit','open','open','','gk_image_show_conf','','','2014-06-22 21:07:32','2014-06-22 21:07:32','',2231,'{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/gk_image_show_conf.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2308,1,'2014-06-22 21:22:30','2014-06-22 21:22:30','The Simplicity theme contains three built-in widgets which can be used for generating content on your website:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"GK Comments\" href=\"{$page_url}/?page_id=758\">GK Comments</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"GK News Show Pro\" href=\"{$page_url}/?page_id=765\">GK News Show Pro</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"GK Tabs\" href=\"{$page_url}/built-in-widgets/gk-tabs/\">GK Tabs</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"GK Tweets\" href=\"{$page_url}/built-in-widgets/gk-tweets/\">GK Tweets</a></li>\r\n